These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, cola
There 2 different types of food: carrot, avocado
The people have 2 different hobbies: video-games, woodworking
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: family, crime
1. the person watching family movies is not to the right of the person eating avocado##8
2. the person eating avocado is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##5
3. the person drinking fanta is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Beverage      | cola     | fanta      |
| Food          | avocado | carrot    |
| Hobby         | woodworking   | video-games |
| Movie-Genre   | family  | crime      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, sprite
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, cooking
The people have 2 different jobs:  coach, police-officer
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, scooter
1. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere to the left of the coach##5
3. the police-officer is not to the right of the coach##8
4. the person driving the motorbike is not the person who's hobby is cooking##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Beverage    | juice        | sprite    |
| Hobby       | board-games         | cooking |
| Job         | police-officer | coach   |
| Transport   | motorbike               | scooter  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, horror
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: salsa, ambient
There are 2 different nationalities: malaysian, egyptian
2 different pets are kept: hamster, frog
1. the malaysian is in an odd position##4
2. the egyptian is not to the right of the owner of the frog##8
3. the fan of salsa is somewhere to the left of the person watching horror movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy       | horror |
| Music-Genre   | salsa       | ambient    |
| Nationality   | malaysian | egyptian |
| Pet           | hamster        | frog   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-4::.
