The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, taxi
1. the turkish is somewhere to the right of the dancer##5
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is not to the left of the person driving the taxi##8
3. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
