There are 2 different nationalities: brazilian, spanish
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, biathlon
The people use 2 different means of transport: train, motorbike
1. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the train##1
2. the brazilian is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
3. the person driving the train is not the person watching animation movies##6
4. the person watching animation movies is not to the right of the person driving the train##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
